now understand each state of the recursive function that i am using
dp[i][j][k] or say rec(s1,s2,k,i,j)
it means whether s1[i..k] and s2[j..k] are scramble strings of each other

now comes the recurrence part 
let us partition 2 string after kth character whre k range[1,len)

for the current 2 strings to be scramble strings of each other 
s1[i..k] and s2[j..k] should be scramble string of each other and
s1[i+k..len] and s2[j+k.len] should be scramble string ofg each other 
this is case one in which after partition we are not swapping to check for scramble string



case2 is that when we swap for after partition  to check for scramble string
in that case the first part of s1 wil be scramble string wth lastpart of s2
and vice versa




